{"tid":396683,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"【剪片需求】剪類似ted-ed片規格需求大概幾多？","createTime":"2017-09-12T00:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T05:54:18.000Z","uid":124449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff66e13e0ea3d4fc2ad636967e9ba8794310410a","tid":396683,"uid":124449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T00:27:37.000Z","msg":"小弟以往都係用~$3K-4K文書Notebook, 唔打機<br />\n讀緊U, 想開 youtube channel拍類似ted-ed既資訊性/教學性片<br />\n香港無咩人拍, sosad <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n爬過文, 好似話剪片係睇CPU/display card &gt; ram/hard disk?<br />\n但照計剪唔同片應該有唔同需求, 小弟唔識點揀  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想拍類似ted-ed片, 1080p夠做, 有少量animation <br />\n示意片: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7yDmGnA8Hw0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7yDmGnA8Hw0&d=B095%2B7ONDbWzZWxw%2F2Nrj54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=57cf8463\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7yDmGnA8Hw0</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N9YLta5Tr2A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DN9YLta5Tr2A&d=B095%2B7ONDbWzZWxw%2F2Nrj54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=2e50ba90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N9YLta5Tr2A</a><br />\n<br />\n請問各位有無notebook推介？ 話說而家做緊大學notebook ownership program<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.lifetat.com/?p=2550\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lifetat.com%2F%3Fp%3D2550&d=B095%2B7ONDbWzZWxw%2F2Nrj54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=83961045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.lifetat.com/?p=2550</a><br />\n<br />\n萬分感激 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048700a9091541a1cb70b768cb9af5d74a8f33db","tid":396683,"uid":124449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T00:37:51.000Z","msg":"講埋筆直, 部laptop &lt;$8000 都可以接受<